videos.description: Baker Mayfield completes a six-yard pass to Mark Andrews for the touchdown to give Oklahoma a quick 7-0 lead over Iowa State.
videos.headline: Oklahoma strikes with early score

videos.description: Baker Mayfield tries to throw, but he's hit and the ball pops up in the air, allowing Iowa State to come up with it and get another turn on offense.
videos.headline: Iowa State comes away with crazy INT against Oklahoma

videos.description: Baker Mayfield gets a pass off to Jeffrey Mead, who shakes off multiple defenders and gets into the end zone for a 30-yard touchdown, giving Oklahoma a 14-3 lead over Iowa State.
videos.headline: Mead puts in extra effort for Oklahoma's second TD

videos.description: Jacob Park throws to Allen Lazard, who gets into the end zone for a 31-yard touchdown, cutting Oklahoma's lead over Iowa State to 14-10.
videos.headline: Iowa State answers back to cut into Oklahoma's lead

videos.description: Joel Lanning gets the ball and breaks through the Sooners' defense for the 41-yard touchdown run to give Iowa State a 17-14 lead over Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Lanning's big run puts Iowa State on top

videos.description: Oklahoma answers Iowa State's go-ahead touchdown with one of its own when Baker Mayfield throws deep to Dede Westbrook, who pushes off his defender for the 65-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Mayfield connects with Westbrook for 65-yard score

videos.description: Baker Mayfield finds Dimitri Flowers for the 11-yard touchdown to give Oklahoma a 28-17 lead over Iowa State going into the half.  It's the fourth touchdown pass of the game for Mayfield.
videos.headline: Mayfield gets his fourth TD pass of the game
